				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Couple of noob questions<a name="24171"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 26 04 7:46 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Weapon skill ups are based on DEX.  I don't know the names of many Shammie buffs, except for some of the bigtime raid buffs.
<br />

<br />
Just /ooc &quot;Heading out to train weapons kills, need a DEX buff, pst&quot;
<br />

<br />
Shammies will have the best ones, I would bet.
<br />

<br />
You can also sing Chant of Battle as your third song, or when you ding 39, Kattas Song of Sword Dancing for DEX.  Keep in mind though, that if your snare or your fear get resisted at all, forget the third song.  Keep them snared and feared are the top priorities, or you will get deaded, and there goes your nice Shammy buff!</span></td>
